author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Carsales.Com Says HY ‍Profit From Ordinary Activities After Tax Attributable Up 27 Pct
text:
Feb 7 (Reuters) - Carsales.Com Ltd:
* HY ‍PROFIT FROM ORDINARY ACTIVITIES AFTER TAX ATTRIBUTABLE TO MEMBERS UP 27% TO A$60.2 MILLION
* HY REVENUE FROM ORDINARY ACTIVITIES $‍200.1 MILLION VERSUS $178.6 MILLION
* 2018 INTERIM DIVIDEND DECLARED 20.5 CENTS‍​ PER SHARE * ‍“WE EXPECT OUR DOMESTIC ADJACENT BUSINESSES TO CONTINUE TO BUILD SCALE AND BREADTH CONSISTENT WITH H1 FY18”​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
